ầu tiên mà Đồng nhắm tới chính là thiếu gia Đường Hạo Phong (Huỳnh Trí Hiền).</p>","tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"97427","season":1,"vote_average":7,"vote_count":1},"modified":"2022-07-05T16:22:39.000Z","cast":["Trương Triệu Huy","Tiêu Chính Nam","Hồng Vĩnh Thành","Ben Wong","Elaine Yiu","Yoyo Chen Chi-Yiu","Trần Oánh"],"director":["Vương Tâm Ủy"],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Trương Triệu Huy","name_vi":"Trương Triệu Huy","name_original":"Eddie Cheung Siu-Fai","tmdb_id":72732,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/jTrBt3y43LsO8XYsQnWg8bdwsP2.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/72732"},{"name":"Tiêu Chính Nam","name_vi":"Tiêu Chính Nam","name_original":"Edwin Siu","tmdb_id":1059226,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/bPEjnmBPWTZcrWQklkqcT1bUQwb.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1059226"},{"name":"Hồng Vĩnh Thành","name_vi":"Hồng Vĩnh Thành","name_original":"Tony Hung","tmdb_id":2214358,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/vsJtcHg5IIOmZTIHrhntjjwZ5zl.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2214358"},{"name":"Ben Wong","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Ben Wong","tmdb_id":1192984,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/yhL5DLBZv4BQIWIZQROvoNGyZuw.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1192984"},{"name":"Elaine Yiu","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Elaine Yiu","tmdb_id":1234807,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/CV05R5HbE4MnpeWeE5HAFaV2bG.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1234807"},{"name":"Yoyo Chen Chi-Yiu","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Yoyo Chen Chi-Yiu","tmdb_id":1240092,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/nMUK7mGsqmxnHJIWtOOrBynV5QG.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1240092"},{"name":"Trần Oánh","name_vi":"Trần Oánh","name_original":"Jeannie Chan","tmdb_id":1206434,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ualtP0ijERgAcWXb2fqWqCnZ6g2.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1206434"}],"keywords":[],"pubjs_url":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/gotvto